<div class="container">

  <div class="header">
    <h1>Peer Review: PRD &mdash; Smart Notification Routing</h1>
    <div class="meta">Audience: VP Product &nbsp;|&nbsp; Stakes: High &nbsp;|&nbsp; Mode: Line-by-line</div>
  </div>

  <div class="verdict">
    <span class="label">Verdict</span>
    Do not send. This is a one-page intent statement, not a PRD, and a VP will return it with the same questions it fails to answer.
